ZH: 请务必在今天之前告知我你是否会来参加派对。
EN: Please inform me whether you will attend the party before today.

ZH: 他已经告知了所有同事他将会离开公司。
EN: He has informed all his colleagues that he will be leaving the company.

ZH: 妈妈告知我要小心穿越马路。
EN: My mom told me to be careful when crossing the street.

ZH: 老师告知我们下周将有一次考试。
EN: The teacher informed us that there will be a test next week.

ZH: 请告知你的航班号码以便我们帮你办理登机手续。
EN: Please inform us of your flight number so we can help you with check-in.

ZH: 我们将会告知您订单号码一旦包裹发货。
EN: We will inform you of the order number once the package is shipped.

ZH: 他们已经告知客户产品推迟发货。
EN: They have informed the customers that the product will be delayed.

ZH: 请告知我你的意见和建议。
EN: Please let me know your opinions and suggestions.

ZH: 这封电子邮件告知了活动的具体细节。
EN: The email informed the details of the event.

ZH: 他们已经告知了公共场所要求的新规定。
EN: They have informed the new regulations required in public places.

ZH: 税务局将会告知你需要准备的文件清单。
EN: The tax office will inform you of the list of documents you need to prepare.

ZH: 请务必告知我你的抵达时间。
EN: Please inform me of your arrival time.

ZH: 酒店前台告知客人可以使用免费泳池。
EN: The hotel front desk informed guests that they can use the free swimming pool.

ZH: 警察告知市民要保持室内外干净。
EN: The police informed citizens to keep both indoor and outdoor areas clean.

ZH: 医生告知患者戒糖的重要性。
EN: The doctor informed the patient about the importance of quitting sugar.

ZH: 他已经告知了所有人我们将会举办一个惊喜聚会。
EN: He has informed everyone that we will be hosting a surprise party.

ZH: 队长告知队员怎样才能提高团队合作能力。
EN: The captain informed the team members on how to improve teamwork.

ZH: 学校通知告知学生下周有一次校外学习活动。
EN: The school notification informed students of an upcoming off-campus learning activity next week.

ZH: 董事会告知员工公司将会进行一次改组。
EN: The board of directors informed employees that the company will undergo a restructuring.

ZH: 请告知你的家人我们将会迟到。
EN: Please inform your family that we will be late.
